Articles.Content:
Hello, I haven't been able to play KSP recently because it would keep crashing every time I tried launching it!

Running in OPenGL mode, Installed mods:

EVE

Astronomers Visual pack V2

Docking Port Alignment indicator

Kerbal Engineer

This is the crash folder:

https://www.dropbox.com/sh/qz79himjmkncla4/AACZDn3oyzTXAhx3vzOY_P1Pa?dl=0

Thank you!

Edited September 5, 2015 by SpaceXray
